# Code Standards

## Follow Established Standards
1. Go Standards
   - Follow [docs/go-standards.md](mdc:docs/go-standards.md)
   - Use standard Go project layout
   - Follow Go best practices

2. Documentation
   - Follow [docs/documentation-standards.md](mdc:docs/documentation-standards.md)
   - Document public APIs
   - Include examples

3. Logging
   - Follow [docs/logging-standards.md](mdc:docs/logging-standards.md)
   - Use structured logging
   - Include context

## Testing Requirements
1. Unit Tests
   - Test individual components
   - Use table-driven tests
   - Mock dependencies

2. Integration Tests
   - Test component interactions
   - Use teatest for TUI testing
   - Test file operations

3. Test Coverage
   - Core timer functionality
   - TUI interactions
   - Lock management